{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-works-work-js","path":"/expore-dana/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"df842167-e829-54a1-ba02-9e101a3322ae","excerpt":"Project Description Explore Wisata is a mini-program running inside the DANA app that lets users buy tickets to travel destinations around…","html":"<h2>Project Description</h2>\n<p><strong>Explore Wisata</strong> is a mini-program running inside the <strong>DANA</strong> app that lets users buy tickets to travel destinations around Bandung — browse, pick a destination, and pay without leaving the wallet.</p>\n<h2>What I did</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Developed the mini-program UI (AXML structure, ACSS layout and styling)</li>\n<li>Built the business logic and pricing calculations in JavaScript</li>\n<li>Integrated the mini-program with the DANA API</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Explore Wisata × DANA","category":"Mini Program Development","tags":["AXML","ACSS","Javascript","Mini Program"],"description":"A mini-program inside the DANA app for buying tickets to travel destinations around Bandung.","projectLink":null,"date":"2021.06.15","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3333333333333333,"src":"/static/5677f02774eae10be522c35fd3152401/73f08/image.png","srcSet":"/static/5677f02774eae10be522c35fd3152401/57fc3/image.png 300w,\n/static/5677f02774eae10be522c35fd3152401/f8eb5/image.png 600w,\n/static/5677f02774eae10be522c35fd3152401/73f08/image.png 1200w,\n/static/5677f02774eae10be522c35fd3152401/51133/image.png 1530w","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/expore-dana/","fileNo":1}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}